何周遭的人和事，都漠不關心市民！<br />\n一.截止選民登記 七月二日前 香港人登記做選民<br />\n防止支持共產黨『高薪低能』敗類滅港<br />\n<br />\n香港真正的抗爭, 是《香港管治權》的爭奪,只有在立法會和區議會選舉, 立法會和區議會選舉議席能否過半, 是管治權的爭奪<br />\n暴政之下，香港人反抗係市民責任、亦係義務<br />\n落實香港自治範圍真實的港人治港，並不是『傀儡雙面人治港』"},{"pid":"61cdf1a0bd20871225544678b583f2828bdd5a78","tid":1215032,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7849f58615b23b5a1c670580b7cc01ff8889ba","tid":1215032,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b31afdeba2897c5c0e6e630ebd4b9ff9e7e355b","tid":1215032,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"提防<br />\n#分化撚<br />\n#消極撚<br />\n#階段勝利撚"}]}